text: Eurasburg is a municipality in Bad Tölz-Wolfratshausen, a district (Landkreis) in Upper Bavaria. It is south of the Bavarian state capital, Munich. == Twin towns == Eurasburg is twinned with: * Rybnik in Poland (since 05.07.2001) ==References== == Other websites == * Eurasburg Official Site Category:Bad Tölz-Wolfratshausen
